quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,40,"Nítorí náà, A mú òun àti àwọn ọmọ ogun rẹ̀. A sì jù wọ́n sínú agbami odò nígbà tí ó jẹ́ alábùkù."
  51,41,"(Àmì tún wà) lára ìjọ ‘Ād. (Rántí) nígbà tí A rán atẹ́gùn ìparun sí wọn."
  51,42,"Kò fi kiní kan tó fẹ́ sí lára sílẹ̀ bẹ́ẹ̀ àfi kí ó sọ ọ́ di n̄ǹkan tó kẹfun.1 {1}",1:[“n̄ǹkan tó kẹfun” ni n̄ǹkan tí ó ti gbó mọ́lẹ̀ tayọ dídámọ̀.]
  52,31,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ máa retí. Dájúdájú èmi náà wà pẹ̀lú yín nínú àwọn olùretí."
  52,32,"Tàbí ọpọlọ wọn ló ń pa wọ́n láṣẹ èyí ni? Tàbí ìjọ alákọyọ ni wọ́n ni?"
  52,33,"Tàbí wọ́n ń wí pé: “Ó dá (al-Ƙur’ān) hun fúnra rẹ̀ ni.” Rárá o, wọn kò gbàgbọ́ ni."
  53,25,"Ti Allāhu sì ni ọ̀run àti ayé."
  53,26,"Àti pé mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn mọlāika tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀, tí ìṣìpẹ̀ wọn kò níí rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀ kiní kan àyàfi lẹ́yìn ìgbà tí Allāhu bá yọ̀ǹda fún ẹni tí Ó bá fẹ́, tí Ó sì yọ́nú sí."
  53,27,"Dájúdájú àwọn tí kò ní ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo nínú Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn, àwọn ni wọ́n ń fún àwọn mọlāika ní orúkọ obìnrin."
  54,16,"Báwo ni ìyà Mi àti ìkìlọ̀ Mi ti rí ná (lára wọn)?"
  54,17,"Dájúdájú A ṣe al-Ƙur’ān ní ìrọ̀rùn fún ṣíṣe ìrántí. Ǹjẹ́ olùrántí wà báyìí bí?"
  54,18,"Ìran ‘Ād pé òdodo ní irọ́. Báwo ni ìyà Mi àti ìkìlọ̀ Mi ti rí ná (lára wọn)?"
  55,10,"Ilẹ̀, (Allāhu) gbé e kalẹ̀ (sí abẹ́ sánmọ̀ fún àwọn ẹ̀dá."
  55,11,"Èso àti dàbínù alápó wà lórí (ilẹ̀)."
  55,12,"Àti èso onípòpórò àti olóòórùn dídùn (wà lórí ilẹ̀)."
  56,1,"Nígbà tí Ìṣẹ̀lẹ̀ (Àjíǹde) bá ṣẹlẹ̀,"
  56,2,"- kò sí irọ́ kan nípa ìṣẹ̀lẹ̀ rẹ̀-"
  56,3,"ó máa mú (àwọn kan) wálẹ̀ (sínú Iná), ó sì máa gbé (àwọn kan) sókè (nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra)."